                                NoCapsLock

        NoCapsLock disables the Caps Lock key. This is to avoid 
accidentally pressing it when typing. You can still use the Shift key, but 
pressing Caps Lock will have no effect. Double-click on the NoCapsLock 
icon to activate it. To exit, double-click on the icon again or use the 
Exchange program (see Utilities/Exchange) to kill it.

       

